data.description: Motivated Sellers!!! Want to look at the stars? This home has a star gazing pad where you can view the sky above all. This home will allow you your space and privacy with plenty of outdoor space and a covered deck and parking for all your toys and vehicles. Upper gate access available as well. The three storage sheds and detached heated and cooled two car garage have plenty of work space and storage space as well. The garage also has 220v. There is an upper patio area above garage as well with birds eye views of the mountains to enjoy. Roof was new in 2019.
